FT  31 DEC 94 / Italian steroid ring uncovered
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By ROBERT GRAHAM
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   ROME
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Italian police have uncovered a countrywide ring distributing illegal
anabolic steroids for body-building. Yesterday, police announced over 120
people were under investigation for trafficking in illicit drugs and their
distribution through health clubs. Some 20 health clubs up and down the
country were being checked and the list is expected to increase.
